{"id":232965399,"title":"過年唰嘴零食 杏仁瓦片 Almond Tuiles 食譜 做法","content":"這次分享的是過年常見的零食-杏仁瓦片，材料跟步驟都相當簡單，自己做不僅省錢又有趣喔~\n這份食譜大概可以做出12-15個，成本不到50元 (依烘焙材料行零售價算，每間店應該差異不大)，希望大家都能動手做做看!\n\n影片版：https://youtu.be/LrPrdGrMaD4\n\n材料：蛋白 1顆、砂糖 30g、低筋麵粉 15g、植物油 20g、杏仁片 80g\n( 植物油可用大豆沙拉油，或葡萄籽油等味道較輕的，不建議使用橄欖油，若要改用奶油也可以 )\n\n步驟：\n1. 盆中加入蛋白和砂糖，用打蛋器均勻攪拌至感覺不到砂糖顆粒， 要避免過度攪拌把蛋白打發 \n2. 加入低筋麵粉和植物油，攪拌均勻\n3. 加入杏仁片，改用橡皮刮刀均勻攪拌，避免杏仁片碎掉\n4. 麵糊放入冰箱，冷藏30-60分鐘\n5. 每一份大約一湯匙，放到烤盤上，再用手和湯匙把麵糊稍微壓平\n6. 烤箱預熱170度，烤12-13分鐘","excerpt":"這次分享的是過年常見的零食-杏仁瓦片，材料跟步驟都相當簡單，自己做不僅省錢又有趣喔~，這份食譜大概可以做出12-15個，成本不到50元 （依烘焙材料行零售價算，每間店應該差異不大），希望大家都能動手做","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"de977130-f3eb-467b-822e-b0e91124e9eb","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-27T05:53:59.732Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-27T05:53:59.732Z","commentCount":4,"likeCount":33,"tags":[],"topics":["過年","零食","做法","食譜","杏仁"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"美食","forumAlias":"food","school":"9巷5弄","department":"alley5lane9","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":33}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":false,"withVideos":false,"media":[],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"42282041-118d-47c4-a54d-fe0ed407eea0","url":"https://img.youtube.com/vi/LrPrdGrMaD4/hqdefault.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://img.youtube.com/vi/LrPrdGrMaD4/hqdefault.jpg","thumbnail":"https://img.youtube.com/vi/LrPrdGrMaD4/hqdefault.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-27T05:53:59.732Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-27T05:53:59.732Z"},{"id":"42282041-118d-47c4-a54d-fe0ed407eea0","url":"https://youtu.be/LrPrdGrMaD4","normalizedUrl":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LrPrdGrMaD4","thumbnail":"https://img.youtube.com/vi/LrPrdGrMaD4/hqdefault.jpg","type":"video/youtube","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"cre